== CODEBASE EXPLORATION RESULTS ==

## Server Crate Structure

### lib.rs (Router)
- Public routes: /health, /ready, /health/idle, /api-keys/bootstrap, /auth/github, /auth/github/callback, /auth/gitlab, /auth/gitlab/callback
- Authenticated routes: /api-keys (CRUD), /identities/:id (GET, PATCH), /identities/:id/auth-status, /identities/:id/repositories
- CORS configured dynamically
- Auth middleware applied to authenticated route group

### AppState
```rust
pub struct AppState {
    pub pool: PgPool,
    pub config: Config,
    pub log_tx: broadcast::Sender<String>,
}
```

### Config
```rust
pub struct Config {
    pub database_url: String,
    pub port: u16,
    pub cors_allowed_origins: Vec<String>,
    pub api_keys: Vec<String>,
    pub worker_stale_seconds: u64,
    pub max_job_reclaims: u32,
    pub job_lease_seconds: u64,
    pub log_retention_days: u32,
    pub chat_history_max_turns: u32,
    // OAuth
    pub github_client_id: Option<String>,
    pub github_client_secret: Option<String>,
    pub github_redirect_uri: Option<String>,
    pub gitlab_client_id: Option<String>,
    pub gitlab_client_secret: Option<String>,
    pub gitlab_redirect_uri: Option<String>,
    pub gitlab_base_url: String,
    pub redirect_after_auth: String,
}
```

### Error handling (AppError)
- Structured JSON errors with status, code, message, details
- Constructors: bad_request, unauthorized, not_found, conflict, forbidden, internal
- Implements IntoResponse for axum
- From<sqlx::Error> for database errors

### Database Schema
- api_keys, identities, personas, workers, sessions, jobs, logs tables
- Identities table has: id, agent_token, git_token, refresh_token, token_expires_at, git_provider, git_base_url, created_at, updated_at
- Default identity seeded with id='default'

### Identity System (from task 06)
- GET /identities/:id returns IdentityStatus (boolean flags only)
- GET /identities/:id/auth-status returns AuthStatus with token health
- PATCH /identities/:id for updating credentials
- GET /identities/:id/repositories for listing repos from GitHub/GitLab
- resolve_credentials() for task credential resolution

### API Types
- IdentityStatus: has_git_token, has_agent_token
- AuthStatus: git_token_status, git_provider, token_expires_at, message
- UpdateIdentityRequest: agent_token?, git_token?, refresh_token?
- ResolvedCredentials: git_token?, agent_token?
- RepositoryInfo: full_name, clone_url
- RepositoryListResponse: items, provider

